Package junit

Class Summary
TestAll This class provides a way to add all testCases and run them together.
TestBroker This class provides a way to test in the scenario of one broker with console interface.
TestBrokerException This class provides a way for exception handling test in the scenario of one broker with console interface.
TestBrokerSwingClients This class provides a way to test in the scenario of one broker with swingRmiClient.
TestBrokerSwingClientsException This class provides a way for exception handling test in the scenario of one broker with swingRmiClient.
TestHeartBeat This class provides a way to test HeartBeat functionality.
TestMultipleBrokers This class provides a way to test in the scenario of multiple brokers with multiple swingRmiClients.
TestMultipleBrokersException This class provides a way for exception handling test in the scenario of multiple brokers.
TestPropertyFileException This class provides a way for exception handling test with property file.
TestTwoBrokers This class provides a way for test in the scenario of two brokers with multiple swingRmiClients.
